Nothing much to describe much about this place, shops floorings are extremely dirty and untidy as I saw rats twice as I visited last month , one was crawling outside the staircase near bus stop entrance/exit and once was practically inside those store,quite a crowded area during meal time and wish authorities would step up to check the hygiene of this coffee shop that health shouldn't be compromised.
